opping Feature). It has a footprint as small as 12.7 mm x 27 mm. Hope it will simplify your overall design/development cycle.</span></span></div><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: var(--secondaryFont); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><img src=\"https://robomartbd.com/uploads/uploads/froala_editor/images/Bluetooth-HC-05_02.png\" style=\"width: 300px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></span><br></p><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: var(--secondaryFont); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"></span></div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: Roboto, serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" id=\"isPasted\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: var(--secondaryFont); box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Packing List:</span></div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text