(28, 'High Torque Gear Motor 12V 100RPM 25GA Price in BD', 800, 30, 830, '12V-100RPM_001.png', 'This easy-to-mount GA25-370 DC Gear motor is great for building robots and it comes in a variety of configurations that suit even the most exigent designs. \r\nThe motor comes in a Small cylinder shape with a diameter of 25 mm a 4mm diameter shaft and 2 Terminal connectors.', 4.80, 'Selver', 50, 9, 1, 730, '<p id=\"isPasted\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Features:&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p>It has a sturdy construction.</p><p>Low Noise</p><p>Shaft equips metal bushes for long life.</p><p>Metal Gears for High performance</p><p>It comes with High-Quality gears.</p><p>High torque at very low Current Consumptions</p><p>Voltage: 12V DC</p><p>RPM:100RPM</p><p>Diameter: 25mm</p><p>Low Noise</p><p>Shaft equips metal bushes for long life.</p><p>Metal Gears for High performance</p><p>It comes with High-Quality gears.</p><p><img src=\"https://robomartbd.com/uploads/uploads/froala_editor/images/12V-100RPM_001.png\" style=\"width: 300px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></p><p id=\"isPasted\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Description</span></strong></p><p>This easy-to-mount GA25-370 DC Gear motor is great for building robots and it comes in a variety of configurations that suit even the most exigent designs.&nbsp;</p><p>The motor comes in a Small cylinder shape with a diameter of 25 mm a 4mm diameter shaft and 2 Terminal connectors.</p><p>Rated voltage: 5-12 (V), Rated current: 0.06 (A), Shaft length: 10 mm/0.4in.</p><p>This DC motor features large moment of force, low speed, and low noise.</p><p>The motor is made of metal gear, wear-resisting, avoid tooth breaking, so with long serving life.</p><p>This motor is adopted of pure copper wire coil, with low heat and low loss.</p><p>Widely used in electronic lock, robot, electric curtain, electric door, micro mixer, monitoring equipment, pet feeding machine</p><p><img src=\"https://robomartbd.com/uploads/uploads/froala_editor/images/12V-100RPM_002.png\" style=\"width: 300px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Package Includes:</span></strong></p><p>1 x High Torque Gear Motor 12V 100RPM 25GA</p><p data-f-id=\"pbf\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;\">Powered by <a href=\"https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1\" title=\"Froala Editor\">Froala Editor</a></p>', '<p data-f-id=\"pbf\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;\">Powered by <a href=\"https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1\" title=\"Froala Editor\">Froala Editor</a></p>', 'Mt-0002'),
