(32, 'Lipo Battery 1000mAh 7.4V 2S Price in BD', 680, 20, 700, 'Lipo-Battery_001.png', 'Voltage:	7.4V\r\nCapacity:	1000mAh\r\nCell Type:	Li-polymer\r\nConfigurations:	2S\r\nContinuous Discharge Rate:25C', 4.70, 'Yellow', 50, 8, 1, 640, '<p id=\"isPasted\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br></span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">FEATURES :</span></strong></p><p>Voltage:<span style=\"white-space:pre;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>7.4V</p><p>Capacity:<span style=\"white-space:pre;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>1000mAh</p><p>Cell Type:<span style=\"white-space:pre;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Li-polymer</p><p>Configurations:<span style=\"white-space:pre;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>2S</p><p>Continuous Discharge Rate:<span style=\"white-space:pre;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>25C</p><p>Max Burst Rate:<span style=\"white-space:pre;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>90C</p><p>Discharge(Output) Lead:<span style=\"white-space:pre;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>T Plug Connector</p><p>Charging(Balancing) Lead:<span style=\"white-space:pre;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>JST-XHR</p><p>Wire Length:<span style=\"white-space:pre;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>100mm</p><p>Operating Temperature Range:<span style=\"white-space:pre;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>-20?to 60?</p><p>PVC color:<span style=\"white-space:pre;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Silver and Black</p><p>Shipment Weight<span style=\"white-space:pre;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>0.078 kg</p><p>Shipment Dimensions<span style=\"white-space:pre;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>8 &times; 5 &times; 4 cm</p><p>Excellent high discharge rate</p><p>Extra-low internal impedance</p><p>Discharge in high-temperature</p><p>Long cycle life and high quality</p><p>Easy customized, energy density</p><p>Low self-discharge etc.</p><p><img src=\"https://robomartbd.com/uploads/uploads/froala_editor/images/Lipo-Battery_001_wFBGo6z.png\" style=\"width: 300px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></p><p id=\"isPasted\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Safety Precautions :</span></strong></p><p>Avoid over-charging or over-discharging the batteries.</p><p>Do n0t put it beside the high-temperature condition.</p><p>Don&rsquo;t throw it into the fire or Water.</p><p><img src=\"https://robomartbd.com/uploads/uploads/froala_editor/images/Lipo-Battery_003.png\" style=\"width: 300px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">DESCRIPTION:</span></strong></p><p>1000mah 2S 30C/60C Lithium Polymer Battery Pack (LiPo) batteries are equipped with heavy-duty discharge leads to minimize resistance and sustain high current loads.</p><p>&nbsp;Batteries stand up to the punishing extremes of aerobatic flight and RC vehicles. Each pack is equipped with gold-plated connectors and JST-XH style balance connectors.</p><p>&nbsp;All Lithium Polymer batteries packs are assembled using IR matched cells</p><p>Lithium Polymer batteries are known for performance, reliability, and price.</p><p>&nbsp;Lithium polymer packs are the go-to pack for those in the know. These batteries deliver the full rated capacity at a price everyone can afford.</p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br></span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">PACKAGE INCLUDES :</span></strong></p><p>1 x Lipo Battery 1000mAh 7.4V 2S.</p><p><br></p><p data-f-id=\"pbf\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;\">Powered by <a href=\"https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1\" title=\"Froala Editor\">Froala Editor</a></p>', '<p data-f-id=\"pbf\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;\">Powered by <a href=\"https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1\" title=\"Froala Editor\">Froala Editor</a></p>', 'BT-0002'),
(33, 'Sound Sensor Module Price in BD', 90, 10, 100, 'Sound_Sensor_001.jfif', 'He sound detection sensor module for Arduino detects whether the sound has exceeded a threshold value. \r\nSound is detected via microphone and fed into an LM393 op-amp. \r\nThe sound level set point is adjusted via an onboard potentiometer.\r\n When the sound level exceeds the set point, an LED on the module is illuminated and the output is sent low.', 4.70, 'Blue', 50, 8, 1, 60, '<p id=\"isPasted\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Features:</span></strong></p><p>Operating voltage 3.3V-5V</p><p>Signal output indication</p><p>Single channel signal output&nbsp;</p><p>Light weight&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Specifications:</span></strong></p><p>Operating voltage 3.3V-5V</p><p>Outputs digital switching output (high and low levels 0 and 1</p><p>Operating current (Vcc=5V): 4-8mA</p><p>Microphone sensitivity (1Khz): 52-48dB</p><p>Microphone Impedance: 2.2K&Omega;</p><p>Microphone Frequency: 16-20Khz</p><p>Microphone S/N ratio: 54dB</p><p>Signal output indication</p><p>Single channel signal output</p><p>Outputs low level and the signal light when there is sound&nbsp;</p><p>Resources:</p><p><br></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Description:</span></strong></p><p>ADIY sound sensor moduleis defined as a module that detects sound waves through their intensity and converts it to electrical signals.&nbsp;</p><p>The sound detection sensor module for Arduino detects whether the sound has exceeded a threshold value.</p><p>Sound is detected via microphone and fed into an LM393 op-amp. The sound level set point is adjusted via an onboard potentiometer.</p><p>When the sound level exceeds the set point, an LED on the module is illuminated and the output is sent low.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">PACKAGE INCLUDES:</span></strong></p><p><br></p><p data-f-id=\"pbf\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;\">Powered by <a href=\"https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1\" title=\"Froala Editor\">Froala Editor</a></p>', '<p data-f-id=\"pbf\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;\">Powered by <a href=\"https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1\" title=\"Froala Editor\">Froala Editor</a></p>', 'SN-004'),
(34, 'GY-9960LLC APDS-9960 RGB and Gesture Sensor Module Price in BD', 350, 30, 380, 'Gesture-Sensor_001.png', 'NT : interrupt output\r\nSCL: I2C clock port\r\nSDA: I2C data port\r\nVCC: power supply positive input port, connect 2.4V-3.6V voltage (3.3V recommended)\r\nGND: power supply negative input\r\nVL: External IR LED power supply. Must be 3.0  4.5V', 4.90, 'Black', 100, 8, 1, 300, '<p id=\"isPasted\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Pin description:</span></strong></p><p>INT : interrupt output</p><p>SCL: I2C clock port</p><p>SDA: I2C data port</p><p>VCC: power supply positive input port, connect 2.4V-3.6V voltage (3.3V recommended)</p><p>GND: power supply negative input</p><p>VL: External IR LED power supply. Must be 3.0 &ndash; 4.5V</p><p><br></p><p id=\"isPasted\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Product parameters:</span></strong></p><p>Working voltage: 2.4V-3.6V</p><p>Measuring range: 4-8in (10-20CM)</p><p>Interface type: I2C interface</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://robomartbd.com/uploads/uploads/froala_editor/images/Gesture-Sensor_001.png\" style=\"width: 300px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></span></p><p id=\"isPasted\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>DESCRIPTION:</strong></span></p><p>The APDS-9960 is an ambient light sensor with integrated ALS, infrared LED and proximity detectors and ambient brightness sensing (ALS, Ambient Light Sensing).</p><p>It uses a dual photodiode to approximate 0.01 lux illumination to approximate the visual response of the human eye.</p><p>Programmable interrupt function with upper and lower thresholds, up to 16-bit resolution for high flexibility even after dark glass,</p><p>proximity sensor fully calibrated for 100 mm object detection, eliminating terminal and sub-components Factory calibration requirements.</p><p>The ambient light dynamic range has also increased from the previous 10K lux to 30K lux, and the solar calibration has been greatly increased to 50K lux,&nbsp;</p><p>which greatly improves the sensitivity and avoids strong light interference.</p><p><img src=\"https://robomartbd.com/uploads/uploads/froala_editor/images/Gesture-Sensor_002.png\" style=\"width: 300px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></p><p>It can work accurately under the large 1.0mm Air Gap without external isolation processing, which greatly facilitates the customer\\&rsquo;s structural design.</p><p>Its wait state power consumption &ndash; 90&mu;A typical, sleep mode power &ndash; 2.2&mu;A typical, more energy efficient;</p><p>up to 400kHz (I2C fast mode) dedicated interrupt pin, I2C interface compatible, fully integrated solution,</p><p>convenient structure and circuit design , I believe that can bring users a better design experience and product value.</p><p id=\"isPasted\"><br></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">PACKAGE INCLUDES:</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">GY-9960LLC APDS-9960 RGB and Gesture Sensor Module</span></p><p data-f-id=\"pbf\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;\">Powered by <a href=\"https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1\" title=\"Froala Editor\">Froala Editor</a></p>', '<p data-f-id=\"pbf\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;\">Powered by <a href=\"https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1\" title=\"Froala Editor\">Froala Editor</a></p>', 'SN-005'),
(35, '12V DC Long-Stroke Linear Actuator 300mm Price in BD', 6750, 250, 7000, '12V-DC_003.png', 'Stroke Length	300mm (apprx. 12inches)\r\nPermanent magnet DC motor drive	Voltage 12VDC\r\nWorking temperature	-20C to +63C\r\nMotor Diameter(mm) 36', 4.90, 'Selver', 10, 8, 1, 6200, '<p id=\"isPasted\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">FEATURES:</span></strong></p><p>Aluminum frame and extension tube</p><p>Compact Design</p><p>Built-in Limit Switch</p><p>Low Noise</p><p>Moisture-proof Surface</p><p>Long life: The drive motor adopts a new carbon brush structure, with a service life of more than 50000 times.</p><p>Permanent magnet DC motor drive: Voltage 12VDC</p><p>Self Locking Force: 500N</p><p><img src=\"https://robomartbd.com/uploads/uploads/froala_editor/images/12V-DC_001.png\" style=\"width: 300px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></p><p id=\"isPasted\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">General Specification :</span></strong></p><p>Stroke Length<span style=\"white-space:pre;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>300mm (apprx. 12inches)</p><p>Permanent magnet DC motor drive<span style=\"white-space:pre;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Voltage 12VDC</p><p>Working temperature<span style=\"white-space:pre;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>-20&ordm;C to +63&ordm;C</p><p>Motor Diameter(mm)<span style=\"white-space:pre;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>36</p><p>Mounting hole diameter (both ends)<span style=\"white-space:pre;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>1/4&rdquo; (6.4mm)</p><p>Protection Level<span style=\"white-space:pre;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>IP55</p><p>Noise level<span style=\"white-space:pre;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>45dB</p><p>Speed at no load<span style=\"white-space:pre;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>15 mm/sec</p><p>Maximum static load<span style=\"white-space:pre;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>110 lbs. (500 Newtons)</p><p>Maximum current draw<span style=\"white-space:pre;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>&le;2A</p><p>Length (mm)<span style=\"white-space:pre;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</s